# TZ-90 — Диалоговая система: единый стандарт из 4 шаблонов с токенами и миграцией существующих диалогов

> ⚠️ **PARTIAL ARCHIVE — Phases A + B only.** This file is the working spec for TZ-90; Phase A (CSS foundation) and Phase B (polymorphic wrapper + service animation trigger) shipped. **Phases C, D, E are still open** and tracked in dedicated sub-tasks:
> - **TZ-90C** — 12 operational dialogs migration to polymorphic wrapper (Layer 3 SERIAL)
> - **TZ-90D** — `/kit/overlays` Section V + TZ-85D `cost-calculation-detail-dialog` wiring (Layer 3 SERIAL)
> - **TZ-90E** — docs sync (`paper-and-ink.md` dialog section, `add-new-page.md` dialog convention) (Layer 1)
>
> The `TZ-90-dialog-system.lock` file's `future_extensions` block lists reserved files for the sub-tasks.
**Дата:** 2026-07-11
**Статус:** ✅ DONE (Phase A + B; Phase C/D/E → TZ-90C/D/E)
**Тип:** cross-cutting (UI standards + tokens + migration 11+ existing dialogs)
**Приоритет:** высокий (явный запрос PO 2026-07-11: «строим продукт, который должен ощущаться как зрелое десктопное приложение»)
**Phases:** A (tokens + shadow/animation) → B (polymorphic wrapper + animation trigger) → C (migration существующих 11+ диалогов) → D (`/kit/overlays` showcase) → E (docs sync)
**LAYER:** Phase A=1, Phase B=2, Phase C=3 (serial), Phase D=3 (serial), Phase E=1
**Зависимости:** TZ-83 ✅ (operational pages существуют → там живут диалоги), TZ-85 IN PROGRESS (TZ-85D = `cost-calculation-detail-dialog` → станет Template 3), TZ-DIALOG-OVERFLOW-FIX rounds 1-5 ✅ (overflow/clip/background правила в `.pi-overlay-panel` ОСТАЮТСЯ)

**CONFLICT KEYS:**
  - frontend/src/app/styles.css
  - frontend/src/app/shared/ui/dialog/pi-dialog.component.ts
  - frontend/src/app/shared/ui/dialog/pi-dialog.service.ts
  - frontend/src/app/shared/ui/dialog/pi-dialog.component.spec.ts
  - frontend/src/app/shared/ui/dialog/pi-alert-dialog.component.ts
  - frontend/src/app/pages/modules/module-form-dialog.component.ts
  - frontend/src/app/pages/work-types/work-type-form-dialog.component.ts
  - frontend/src/app/pages/products/product-form-dialog.component.ts
  - frontend/src/app/pages/contracts/contract-form-dialog.component.ts
  - frontend/src/app/pages/materials/material-form-dialog.component.ts
  - frontend/src/app/pages/orders/order-form-dialog.component.ts
  - frontend/src/app/pages/organizations/organization-form-dialog.component.ts
  - frontend/src/app/pages/modules/module-materials-form-dialog.component.ts
  - frontend/src/app/pages/products/product-module-picker-dialog.component.ts
