### Phase B — Wrapper polymorphic + animation trigger (TZ-90B, **Layer 2**)

**Цель:** `<app-pi-dialog>` понимает 4 variants + animation trigger из service.

**Подзадачи:**

1. **B.1** `pi-dialog.component.ts`:
   - Add `variant = input<'alert'|'form'|'content'|'destructive'>('form')`.
   - Add `xl` в `width` input enum.
   - Compute `panelClass()` per variant+width. **Canonical 4×4 таблица** (НЕ ДОЛЖНО расходиться ни в одной комбинации):

| variant × width | `panelClass()` canonical string |
|---|---|
| alert × sm       | `'bg-paper rounded-sm w-[360px] flex flex-col'` |
| alert × md       | NOT SUPPORTED — use only if title very long |
| alert × lg       | NOT SUPPORTED — Alert должен stay compact |
| alert × xl       | NOT SUPPORTED — Alert должен stay compact |
| form × sm        | `'bg-paper rounded-sm w-[360px] flex flex-col'` (rare; 1-2 fields only) |
| form × md        | `'bg-paper rounded-sm w-[480px] flex flex-col'` |
| form × lg        | `'bg-paper rounded-sm w-[640px] flex flex-col'` (default) |
| form × xl        | `'bg-paper rounded-sm w-[800px] flex flex-col'` (very wide forms) |
| content × sm     | NOT SUPPORTED — Content requires room |
| content × md     | NOT SUPPORTED — Content requires room |
| content × lg     | NOT SUPPORTED — prefer xl for content |
| content × xl     | `'bg-paper rounded-sm max-w-[800px] flex flex-col'` (default for T3) |
| destructive × sm | NOT SUPPORTED — Destructive requires visual weight |
| destructive × md | `'bg-paper rounded-sm w-[480px] flex flex-col'` (default for T4) |
| destructive × lg | `'bg-paper rounded-sm w-[640px] flex flex-col'` (rare; long warning text) |
| destructive × xl | NOT SUPPORTED — Destructive должен stay focused |

   - `bodyClass`, `headerClass`, `footerClass`: variant-driven padding (alert = компактнее padding 12px на header; form = 24px; content = 24px + sticky opt-in). **Canonical mapping**:
     - alert header: `flex items-center justify-between hairline-b px-4 py-3`
     - form header: `flex items-center justify-between hairline-b px-6 py-4`
     - content header: `flex items-center justify-between hairline-b px-6 py-4`
     - destructive header: same + `<lucide-angular [img]="AlertTriangle" [size]="18" class="text-destructive mr-2" />` prefix on title
     - alert body: `px-4 py-3 text-sm text-ink`
     - form body: `px-6 py-6 text-sm text-ink`
     - content body: `px-6 py-6 text-sm text-ink overflow-y-auto`
     - destructive body: `px-6 py-6 text-sm text-ink`
     - all variants footer: `hairline-t px-6 py-4 flex justify-end gap-3 items-center`
     - content footer: same + `position: sticky; bottom: 0; background: var(--dialog-bg);`
   - Animation: принимает input `animate = true` (default); через class-binding на root `<div role="dialog">` добавляет `pi-dialog-host-open`.

2. **B.2** `pi-dialog.service.ts`:
   - Получаем overlayElement после `attach()`.
   - Find `[role="dialog"]` (the inner of `<app-pi-dialog>`).
   - Add `.pi-dialog-host-open` класс.
   - DialogConfig: extend `{ modal: true }`, `width: 'sm'|'md'|'lg'|'xl' | string` (xl=800), keep others as is.

3. **B.3** `pi-dialog.component.spec.ts` update:
   - Tests для каждого variant: panelClass snapshot, default width, animation opt-in.

4. **B.4** Verify: `pnpm exec jest --testPathPattern=pi-dialog.component.spec.ts` exit 0. Frontend typecheck exit 0.

**Acceptance criteria:**
- All 4 variants рабочих (visual smoke через Phase D).
- Width xl даёт до 800px.
- Animation 180ms ease-out, disabled по `prefers-reduced-motion`.

