8. **C.8** `module-materials-form-dialog.component.ts` → wrap (new).
9. **C.9** `pi-alert-dialog.component.ts` → verify wrap с `variant="alert"`.
10. **C.10** `product-module-picker-dialog.component.ts` → wrap `variant="content" width="xl"`.
11. **C.11** `text-block-dialog.component.ts` → wrap `variant="content" width="xl"`.
12. **C.12** `table-template-dialog.component.ts` → wrap `variant="content" width="xl"`.

**Acceptance criteria:**
- Audit Table (§3) 13/13 marked ✅ post-completion.
- Browser smoke на каждой странице checkbox: `/products` → Create Product → opens form dialog (shadow + dimmed + rounded); и т.д.
